&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://mael-zys.github.io/PhysMoDPO/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Project Page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
